<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id279dbcd8-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419" identifier="/us/usc/t45/s162"><num value="162">§ 162.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for expenditure by the Mediation Board in carrying out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id279dbcd9-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419">(<ref href="/us/act/1926-05-20/ch347/s12">May 20, 1926, ch. 347, § 12</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/587">44 Stat. 587</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1934-06-21/ch691/s7">June 21, 1934, ch. 691, § 7</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/48/1197">48 Stat. 1197</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id279dbcda-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419">
