<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id279dbcdc-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1934—Act <date date="1934-06-21">June 21, 1934</date>, substituted “Mediation Board” for “Board of Mediation”.</p>
